give examples; poe

Ease
Dont want to go through that extra 2 mins.

And hence we win.

- Why do I think People use ellie.mercari.in
- Vision for Ellie
- Dump of open source tools
- Why because people use ellie for 5 mins of ease > why wont they use these tools because the a barrier of entry is 6 hours of work on average to set this tools up.

This data science guy is missing and it is repalced with anyone (as long as they can write the prompt) - We are going to partner with Mercari blog team to see how we can help them.

This also ties into the idea that we can move fast individually or we can move relatively slower but moving the whole company forward. Google Maps vs Japanese Nav Tools
